data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled on a spacious 24.5-acre lot. This immaculate property offers the perfect blend of luxury living and rural tranquility. Inside, you'll find a well-appointed interior with ample space for comfortable living and entertaining. The home features a modern kitchen, inviting living areas, and spacious bedrooms. One standout feature is the RV bay, providing convenient storage for all your recreational vehicles and outdoor gear. Outside, the expansive acreage offers endless possibilities. Whether you're looking to explore nature, start a hobby farm, or simply enjoy the peace and quiet, this property has it all. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule a showing today!
